</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【實試】MSI Crosshair 15 Rainbow 6 Edition 電競手提電腦　 聯乘設計獨特 + NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 獨顯</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/05/msi-crosshair-15-rainbow-6/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=msi-crosshair-15-rainbow-6</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[小白]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 05 May 2022 09:20:01 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[買物情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[Crosshair 15]]></category><category><![CDATA[Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition]]></category><category><![CDATA[MSI]]></category><category><![CDATA[電競]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098217</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>喜歡玩第一身視角射擊遊戲的朋友，應該都會玩過 Rainbow Six 吧！甚至乎是「R6」的粉絲。玩第一身射擊 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>喜歡玩第一身視角射擊遊戲的朋友，應該都會玩過 Rainbow Six 吧！甚至乎是「R6」的粉絲。玩第一身射擊遊戲最緊要是反應要快，當中有強勁硬件配合就事半功倍，如果連整臺手提電腦都是「R6」的主題，打機應該會更起勁吧！MSI 早前就推出了 Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six Extraction <a href="https://hkstore.msi.com/pages/msi-rtx30-crosshair-pulse-gl">限量聯名特仕版的 Crosshair 15 B12UEZ</a>，如果你正是筆者口中的 R6 迷，而又打算換新手提電腦提升打機體驗的話，就要看看筆者今次的評測了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_01.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098236" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_01-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_01-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_01-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_01-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_01-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_01.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2><strong>植入大量 Rainbow Six：Extraction </strong><strong>元素</strong></h2><p>既然是限量聯名特仕版，<a href="https://hkstore.msi.com/pages/msi-rtx30-crosshair-pulse-gl">Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition</a>機身當然加入了大量 Rainbow Six：Extraction 元素。從機面可看到機身是以黑加黃為主調，正是以「外來生物分析與收容虹彩小隊（REACT）」作為設計靈感：機面除了間紋之外更有由小隊徽章加地圖融合而成的 Logo，打開手提電腦亦可以看到小隊 Logo 以及觸控板上的 REACT 字樣，將遊戲中經典場景與元素一一呈現於機體外觀上面，相當獨特大膽而且型格。不單如此，限量聯名特仕版更附送聯名限量滑鼠、滑鼠墊與 Rainbow Six ：Extraction 豪華版遊戲序號，單是以上的排場都足以吸引 Rainbow Six 粉絲入手吧！</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_02.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098235" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_02-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_02.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 雖然是黑色為主調，但融入了 Rainbow Six：Extraction 的黃色主色，令整機有著強烈對比，極之型格。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_04.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098233" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_04-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_04-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_04-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_04.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機面的小隊徽章加地圖融合而成的 Logo。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_05.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_05-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_05-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_05-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_05.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵盤位置使用了黃至黑漸變營造出科幻效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_06.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_06-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_06-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_06-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_06.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵盤右下角植入了的 REACT 小隊徽章。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_07.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_07-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_07-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_07-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_07.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲就連觸控板也加入了 REACT 字樣及條碼，相當有型，同時可見這塊觸控板的大小隻算適中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_08.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_08-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_08-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_08-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_08.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲附送聯名滑鼠墊。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_09.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_09-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_09-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_09-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_09.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲附送聯名限量滑鼠屬有線設計。</p><h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>WASD </strong><strong>四鍵使用搶眼黃色透明鍵帽</strong></h2><p>以往多款高階的 MSI 手提電腦也配備 RGB 鍵盤，今回 Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 配備了科幻感與實用性兼備的「炫彩光譜電競鍵盤」。此鍵盤為孤島式設計屬 1.7mm 鍵程，實際輸入手感不錯，100% 鍵盤具備 Num Pad 設計，加上多個快速鍵，一般使用以及打機時的體驗相當滿意。更特別的地方在於鍵盤背光並不是一般的 RGB，而是黃、藍、綠三色，特別之餘更在玩 FPS 遊戲中最常用的 WASD 四個鍵上使用了黃色透明鍵帽，讓大家一眼就辨識得出位置，充滿電競味道。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_10.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_10-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲屬 100% 設計的鍵盤並不是一般的 RGB，而是黃、藍、綠三色，極為特別。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_11.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲WASD 四個鍵上使用了黃色透明鍵帽，讓大家一眼就辨識得出位置，充滿電競味道。</p><h2><strong>I/O </strong><strong>數量不過不失</strong></h2><p>MSI 電競手提電腦的介面配置一向不錯，而 Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 其 I/O 數量與佈局筆者認為是中規中矩。機身左邊備有火牛插位及兩個 USB-A，其中一個為 USB 2.0 規格；至於右邊則備有一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-A 介面、一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-C、Full-Size HDMI 及 LAN 介面，當然亦有耳機與咪高峰二合一插孔。雖然介面數量算足夠，但如果配備 Thunderbolt 4 就會在擴充上更添便利。另一特別之處是機身有一個 USB 2.0，用來兼容較舊的 USB 裝置，但其實可以的話全數是 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-A 就會比較好。另外，Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 的 USB-PD 不支援充電功能，帶去其他地方玩時記得要執好火牛。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_12.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_12-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_12-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_12-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_12.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身左邊備有兩個 USB-A，其中一個為 USB 2.0 規格。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_13.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_13-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_13-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_13-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_13.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲右邊則備有一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-A 介面、一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-C、HDMI 及 LAN 介面，當然亦有耳機 / 咪高峰插孔。。</p><h2><strong>GeForce RTX 3050 Ti </strong><strong>獨立顯示卡搭配 Intel </strong><strong>第 12 </strong><strong>代 Core </strong><strong>處理器</strong></h2><p>作為電競手提電腦，Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 搭載第 12 代 Intel Core i7-12700H 處理器，為 14 核心（6 個 P-Cores 加 8 個 E-Cores） 20 線程規格，以及內置有 6GB 記憶體的 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 獨立顯示卡。這個高效組合可預期會發出一定的熱量，尤其是打機時系統全速運行的話，若做不好散熱就有機會令效能下降，因此廠方於 Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 機體內使用雙散熱模組設計的 Cooler Boost 5，雙風扇搭配最多 6 組熱導管，確保機內廢熱可於機側及背面的位置排走。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_14.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_14-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_14-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_14-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_14.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機體使用 Cooler Boost 5 散熱模組，處理器及獨立顯示卡的熱量由機身後方及側邊排出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_15.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_15-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_15-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_15-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_15.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲從機底的六角形大型入風口可見 Cooler Boost 5 散熱模組具備多條散熱管。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_16.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098221" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_16-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_16-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_16-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_16.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左右各一把風扇將機內熱力快速帶走。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_19.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098618" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_19-694x487.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="487" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_19-694x487.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_19-1280x898.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_19-768x539.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_19.jpg 1355w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可使用 3D 環繞 Nahimic 遊戲音效。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_20.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1098619 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_20-694x424.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="424" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_20-694x424.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_20-1280x782.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_20-768x469.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_20-1536x938.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_20.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新設計的 MSI Center 收藏所有專屬功能，將監控、調整與優化等多種實用功能都整合為一。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_21.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_21-582x580.jpg" alt="" width="582" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_21-582x580.jpg 582w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_21-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_21.jpg 605w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 582px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲搭載第 12 代 Intel Core i7-12700H 處理器，屬 14 核心 20 線程設計。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22-694x480.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="480" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22-694x480.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22-1280x885.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22-768x531.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22-1536x1062.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22-2048x1416.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_22.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配備 16GB RAM 下，PCMark 得分為 7442 分。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098617" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23-694x480.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="480" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23-694x480.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23-1280x885.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23-768x531.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23-1536x1062.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23-2048x1416.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_23.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內置 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 獨立顯示卡，3DMark Time Spy 得分為 8903 分，效能令人滿意。</p><h2><strong>IPS-Level </strong><strong>屏幕高解像度兼達 165Hz </strong><strong>更新率</strong></h2><p>Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 主攻打機玩家，除了強大處理器及獨立顯示卡之外，另一樣重要就是屏幕。Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 的 15.6 吋為 IPS-Level 屏幕，而且達 QHD 解像度以及達到了 165Hz 更新率。實測這個屏幕流暢度相當不錯，平時睇片的效果相當不俗，當然打機時可以有精緻、流暢和清晰的視覺效果。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_17.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098613" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_17-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_17-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_17-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_17.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲15.6 吋 IPS-Level 屏幕畫質相當好，顏色表現不會太濃。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_18.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_18-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_18-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/MSI-Crosshair-15-B12UEZ_18.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援 165Hz 更新率，帶來流暢打機體驗。</p><h2>總結：</h2><p>配備第 12 代 Intel Core i7-12700H 處理器、內置 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 獨立顯示卡，亦有 144Hz IPS-Level 屏幕，Crosshair 15 B12UEZ Rainbow 6 Edition 的效能足以應付打機以至日常使用，當然最重要是與 Rainbow Six：Extraction 聯名，外觀型格還隨送獨家配件，而且目前 MSI 網上商店更進行消費券優惠，此機減至$14,999（<a href="https://hkstore.msi.com/pages/msi-rtx30-crosshair-pulse-gl">購買連結</a>），如再去 MSI HK 的 Facebook 或 IG 上貼文，更有機會獲得額外 $1,000 優惠代碼（限量 30 組），買機自然更抵。</p></p><div class="feedflare">
